Consob Says UniCredit, Cariverona Lists for Mediobanca Linked

-- B y   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 
2011-10-20T05:59:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/consob-says-unicredit-cariverona-lists-for-mediobanca-linked.html
Italy’s market regulator Consob
ruled that lists presented by  UniCredit SpA (UCG)  and Fondazione
Cariverona for Mediobanca’s statutory auditors board are linked,
according to a statement sent through the Italian exchange late
yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Bertacche at 
 mbertacche@bloomberg.net  